{"tid":2205253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美司法部控5中國人涉入侵全球逾百企業 香港民主派人士也中招","createTime":"2020-09-16T16:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T18:40:07.000Z","uid":239336,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f903287e873e030b875a4be9c6a9f1a1e24e3a8f","tid":2205253,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"美國司法部周三起訴5名中國人和兩名馬來西亞人，指他們涉嫌在過去至少6年進行全球性黑客活動，入侵美國及各地共逾100間企業，包括軟件開發公司、電腦硬件製造商、電訊公司、社交媒體、電子遊戲公司、非政府組織、大學、智庫和外國政府的網絡，並曾入侵香港民主派政治人物和活躍分子的賬戶，監視他們的活動。<br />\n<br />\n司法迎指該黑客集團並非由中國政府營運，但其中一名黑客自稱受到中國國安部門的保護。司法部官員表示一些黑客認為他們與中國政府的聯繫，讓他們可隨意在全球進行黑客活動，偷取訊息和技術。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府早前指控中國涉及網絡犯眾，7月時檢察官指出，有與中國政府合作的黑客，針對研發武漢肺炎疫苗的企業發動網絡攻擊，從全球各地公司竊取價值數百萬美元的的知識產權和商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200917/JRYBEZEIKNCQHD57WQ4EEUUIGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200917%2FJRYBEZEIKNCQHD57WQ4EEUUIGE%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=a1c4c92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200917%2FJRYBEZEIKNCQHD57WQ4EEUUIGE%2F&h=b2909eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200917/JRYBEZEIKNCQHD57WQ4EEUUIGE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db873c83c7aab81d9f1ef1bd1d9a191554836c2","tid":2205253,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ef91a41011127799ba3c3951f73a69581138bc","tid":2205253,"uid":338439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"出兵打佢啦屌佢老母"},{"pid":"af294c93dd2c108cea1afc651